('Valette Foie Gras', 'Saint Clair', '46300', 'Gourdon', '法国', '565416176', 'www.valette.com', 'Valette Foie Gras is a 3rd generation family business, created by the grandfather of Mr. Jacques Valette in 1920.  The main objective was, and still is, to produce high quality Foie Gras.  Over the past years, Valette Foie Gras has created a range of more than 350 different products ? Duck Foie Gras, Goose Foie Gras, traditional and innovative cooked dishes, and continually develops new products whilst respecting the old traditional art of cooking .\r\n\r\nThe Valette Group currently processes and markets 1,300,000 IGP-approved Perigord ducks. In 2008 Valette obtained 3 new medals at the ?Concours Général Agricole? of Paris, making a total of 30 medals in 20 years.\r\n\r\n Today Valette Foie Gras is a leading group in the Foie Gras market.  With a workforce of 220 in 2011 the Group?s turnover was almost 50 ? Million.   \r\n\r\n', 'BRYGGEMANN', 'NINA', 'NINA BRYGGEMANN', 'nina-bryggemann@valette.com', '', '', '即食菜肴（新鲜、冷冻或罐头菜肴） - 精致香料产品 - 家禽肉类（鲜肉和冻肉）、鸡蛋、野味', '非洲 - 南美洲 - 亚洲 - 欧洲 - 东欧 - 北欧- 南欧 - 大洋洲 -其他', '南非 - 德国 - 澳大利亚 -比利时 - 加勒比地区 - 智利 - 韩国 - 丹麦 - 西班牙 - 瓜德罗普岛 - 香港 -印度 - 冰岛-意大利 - 日本 - 法国 - 摩纳哥 - 新西兰 - 荷兰- 菲律宾 - 法属波利尼西亚 -捷克 -留尼汪岛- 罗马尼亚 -英国 - 俄罗斯 - Saint Martin - 新加坡 - 瑞士 - 多哥 - 越南', '2013-12-19 14:45:00', '2013-12-19 14:45:00'),
