(263, 1, '2014-08-20 18:37:51', '2014-08-20 10:37:51', 'TheWineIndustryAssociationof WeaternAustralia, Linkar Group and Guangdong Guangxin Information Technology Industry Development Co., Ltd jointly announced the establishment of ITS Australia Anti-Counterfeiting Track andTrace Certification Center. So far, hundreds of high-end wine brands from more than 400 vineyards in Western Australia have been included into the ITS development catalogue. The ITS platform will enable supervision departments in Guangdong to access a range of data related to each bottle of wines, providing safe green door for Chinese consumers to track and trace wines from vineyards in Western Australia.\r\n日前，西澳酒协、西澳农业推荐的澳大利大林卡集团与广东广新信息技术产业发展公司联合宣布，共同成立ITS澳大利亚防伪溯源认证中心，目前西澳400多家酒庄的数百个高端葡萄酒品牌已被纳入ITS发展的名录。ITS平台还将与广东酒类监管部门联网、对接，使广东监管部门也可能过该平台获得每一瓶酒的来源、产供销及流向信息，从而实现源头监管、跟踪溯源，为中国消费者打开直通西澳酒庄的安全绿色之门。', 'talk1', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'talk1', '', '', '2014-09-01 12:51:37', '2014-09-01 04:51:37', '', 0, 'http://wordpress.local/?p=263', 0, 'post', '', 0),
